org.opendaylight.yang.gen.v1.urn.opendaylight.packet.ipv4.rev140528

Interface Ipv4PacketFields

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataContainer, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject, PacketFields
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Ipv4Packet

    public interface Ipv4PacketFields
extends org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject, PacketFields

    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module ipv4-packet 

     grouping ipv4-packet-fields {
     leaf version {
         type uint8;
     }
     leaf ihl {
         type uint8;
     }
     leaf dscp {
         type dscp;
     }
     leaf ecn {
         type uint8;
     }
     leaf ipv4-length {
         type uint16;
     }
     leaf id {
         type uint16;
     }
     leaf reserved-flag {
         type boolean;
     }
     leaf df-flag {
         type boolean;
     }
     leaf mf-flag {
         type boolean;
     }
     leaf fragment-offset {
         type uint16;
     }
     leaf ttl {
         type uint8;
     }
     leaf protocol {
         type known-ip-protocols;
     }
     leaf checksum {
         type uint16;
     }
     leaf source-ipv4 {
         type ipv4-address;
     }
     leaf destination-ipv4 {
         type ipv4-address;
     }
     leaf ipv4-options {
         type binary;
     }
     leaf payload-offset {
         type int32;
     }
     leaf payload-length {
         type int32;
     }
 }
    The schema path to identify an instance is ipv4-packet/ipv4-packet-fields
